column1: Table 7-20:  U.S. Pulp and Paper(a), Meat, Poultry, Vegetables, Fruits and Juices, Ethanol, Breweries, and Petroleum Refining Production (MMT)
(a) Pulp and paper production is the sum of market pulp production plus paper and paperboard production.

Sources: Pulp and Paper - FAO (2020a) and FAO (2020b); Meat, Poultry, and Vegetables - USDA (2020a and 2020c); Ethanol - Cooper (2018) and RFA (2020a and 2020b); Breweries - Beer Institute (2011) and TTB (2020); Petroleum Refining - EIA (2020).
